The staff at Le Vuong Guesthouse looks forward to serving you during your upcoming visit.

Description: Located on the most vibrant road in Phu Quoc, just a 10-minute walk from Duong Dong beach, Hoi An Retreat Phu Quoc is located on a hillside, surrounded by forests and sea breezes. heavenly dome.  Hoi An Retreat Phu Quoc is a 3-star luxury resort, with a population of 28 fully-equipped and extremely charming bungalows, secretly bearing the architecture of Hoi An Ancient Town. The heart of the resort is the cool 4-season spring pool, spread along the sidewalks on both sides of the street, like a river crossing the old town on a sunny autumn day. The overall space creates romantic views to sob, and touches deeply to the soul.  Hoi An Retreat Phu Quoc harmonizes with flowers and plants, nurturing so many wandering souls; I cherish the love of couples; forging and warming family affection; guide the soul between mother nature and to find a healing experience.  The distance from Hoi An Retreat Phu Quoc to Sun Set Bar Beach is 10 minutes on foot (900 meters), 10 minutes by car from the airport, 2.4 kilometers from the Central Night Market, 25 kilometers from the North Island, and 23 kilometers from the South Island.  Hoi An Resort has alacarte service, coffee, tea, juice served in the room. Motorbike rental service 150k/day, self-drive 5-seater car 600k/day, dry cleaning service 50k/kg, laundry 50k/unit. Airport pick-up one-way 5-seat car 110k/trip, resort taxi 15k/km.  Returning to Hoi An is going home. It's because, "Home Is Where Your Heart Is".
